      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LUXIO WAVE (1) collided with another runner and finished a well held 6 lengths sixth (23.00) last time in a Mix 5 at this track over 400m. Little luck latest and can bounce back to best. IMPRESS ROCKS (2) was below latest but prior to that a Mix 5 winner in quick time (22.72) at this track in a Mix 5. Well placed here and should do much better. YUNDERUP SUN (4) boxed on well to finish second last time, beaten a neck (22.59) behind Send It Kye at this track. Ran one of the fastest times on the program last start despite finishing in the minors. Hard to beat again. PRINCESS MILA (8) is a last-start placegetter at this track and distance - in the mix again.",
